These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, cat, hamster, bird
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, bluemaster, pall-mall, bolivar
4 different games are played: domino, whist, mah-jongg, chess
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, raspberry, mango, peas
 1. the person playing whist is not to the right of the person playing domino##8
 2. the person eating nectarine is not to the left of the person eating nectarine##8
 3. the person eating peas is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person playing domino is not to the left of the person playing chess##8
 5. the person eating nectarine is not to the right of the person eating nectarine##8
 6. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 7. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
 8. the bolivar-smoker is between the person eating raspberry and the person playing whist##2
 9. the person eating peas is the pall-mall-smoker##1
10. the person eating peas is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
11. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3
12. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
13. the pall-mall-smoker is not to the left of the person eating peas##8
14. the owner of the cat is the person eating mango##1
15. the owner of the cat is not the person playing whist##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Pet         | goldfish     | cat   | bird | hamster |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | bolivar   | alhambra   | pall-mall  |
| Game         | whist  | mah-jongg  | chess  | domino |
| Food     | nectarine    | mango | raspberry     | peas    |

