 4. the person traveling to rome is not to the right of the palace house##8
 5. the modern house is not to the left of the chaman-smoker##8
 6. the person who likes lilac is not to the right of the person traveling to boston##8
 7. the craftsman house is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5
 8. the craftsman house is in an odd position##4
 9. the alhambra-smoker is the victorian house##1
10. the baccarat-smoker is on the left or right of the modern house##3
11. the modern house is not to the left of the baccarat-smoker##8
12. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
13. the dunhill-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who likes azure##5
14. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the baccarat-smoker##3
15. the person traveling to rome is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
17. the person traveling to rome is not to the right of the chaman-smoker##8
18. the person who likes azure is not to the right of the victorian house##8
