 4. the person drinking fanta is between the person who growszinnia and the person who growsiris##2
 5. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
 6. the person traveling to venice is not to the right of the person drinking fanta##8
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4
 8. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the airplane##5
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
