10. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person eating peach##1
11. the person who growsazalea is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
13. the person eating lemon is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##8
14. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##8
15. the person who's birthday is in may is the person driving the tram##1
16. the person who's birthday is in august is not to the right of the person driving the boat##8

.:: Answer ::.
